
### **3. `install.sh`** (Simple installer)
```bash
#!/bin/bash
# Simple installer for PySSLScan

echo "Downloading PySSLScan..."
curl -o pysslscan.py https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yourusername/pysslscan/main/pysslscan.py
chmod +x pysslscan.py

echo "Installation complete!"
echo "Run: python pysslscan.py example.com"
